Package org.jcatapult.mvc.parameter.convert

Interface Summary
AnnotationConverter<T extends Annotation> Converters are used to convert objects from one type to another, convert strings to objects and to convert from objects and strings to arrays of objects.
ConverterProvider This interface defines the method of getting Converters.
GlobalConverter Converters are used to convert objects from one type to another, convert strings to objects and to convert from objects and strings to arrays of objects.
 

Class Summary
AbstractAnnotationConverter<T extends Annotation> This class is the base type converter for all the annotaiton type converters that handle Object types.
AbstractGlobalConverter This class is the base type converter for all the type converters that handle Object types.
DefaultConverterProvider This class is the manager for all the Converters.
 

Exception Summary
ConversionException This is a runtime exception thrown when type conversion fails.
ConverterStateException This is a runtime exception thrown when the state of the current conversion is such that conversion can never proceed.
